# Magic Markup: Maintaining Document-External Markup with an LLM

This file is a transition-time build anchor for the public page.
The canonical publication record and assets live in
`pubs/2024-programming-magicmarkup/`.

Edit `pubs/2024-programming-magicmarkup/publication.json` for structured
publication data, keep the abstract/BibTeX/assets in the same directory, and
use `pubs/2024-programming-magicmarkup/extra.dj` for any rare page-specific
extra content.
